Sentencas: Commercial La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta powder was used for preparation of corresponding perovskite films on commercial Crofer 22 APU high chromium steel by pulsed laser deposition.
Titulo: Physicochemical properties of the Crofer 22 APU steel with La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ protective-conductive coatings prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: The obtained films PLD1 and PLD2 with a thickness of 1.1 and 0.35 mu m, respectively, were dense and homogeneous, with good adhesion to the polished surface.
Titulo: Physicochemical properties of the Crofer 22 APU steel with La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ protective-conductive coatings prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: Oxidation studies of the samples were carried out in air at 800 degrees C for 200 h. The calculated parabolic rate constant kp after isothermal oxidation for the PLD1 sample was 4.10x10-14 g2cm-4s- 1and was approximately four times lower than the oxidation rate determined for the PLD2 sample.
Titulo: Physicochemical properties of the Crofer 22 APU steel with La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ protective-conductive coatings prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: As a result of the oxidation process, in both cases, a thin oxide layer of chromia and Mn1.5Cr1.5O4 spinel was formed on the steel/film interface.
Titulo: Physicochemical properties of the Crofer 22 APU steel with La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ protective-conductive coatings prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: In addition, small amounts of manganese-chromium spinel crystals were observed on the films' surfaces.
Titulo: Physicochemical properties of the Crofer 22 APU steel with La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ protective-conductive coatings prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: Values of the specific electrical resistance at 800 degrees C after 100 h of the experiment were 0.06 and 0.038 ohm center dot cm2 for PLD1 and PLD2, respectively.
Titulo: Physicochemical properties of the Crofer 22 APU steel with La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ protective-conductive coatings prepared by pulsed laser deposition

Sentencas: Results indicate that the applied coatings meet the criteria set upon protective-conductive layers for interconnect materials, for the ITSOFCs (intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells) applications.
Titulo: Physicochemical properties of the Crofer 22 APU steel with La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ protective-conductive coatings prepared by pulsed laser deposition
